?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><font color=\"#ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size:36px;\"><b>\"이건 기적이다\"</b></span></font></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>공략 하기 앞서 크라운이 없어 정말 꼬운 보스 최강자였음.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>7줄 남기고 전멸, 12줄남기고 시간초과, 별에 별 짓을 다해봤음.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>근데 그냥 레후 잘키웠으니 1버를 라피 고정하고 신데 레후로 버스트 굴렸으면&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>어땟을까 생각들긴 들었지만 내가 만들고있는 택틱이 있었어서 생각없이 트라이만 했던거같음...</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>쨋든 왜 이번 공략에 크라운이 없으면 힘든가... 를 설명하기 위해서는&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">이론이 중요함.</span></b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이론 설명</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>대부분의 버스트는 스킬 쓴 직후 10초간만 효과 유지가 대부분임.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>라피 1스킬의 경우 10초간 시공증, 그브도 10초 공증.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>하지만 크라운은? 버스트에 무려 15초 공증이 존재함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이게 중요한게, 크라운이 있으면 그냥 상시 공증이 켜지는거와 마찬가지임.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>우리가 버스트를 빠르게 따다닥 쓰는 이유도 풀버시간이 10초인데,</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이때 한번에 많은 딜을 우겨넣기 위해 공증+버프의 지속시간이 딱&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>맞아 떨어지게 하기 위해 버스트 연타를 하는거임.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>또한 베히모스는 따발총 패턴이 있기때문에 베리어가 없는게 진짜 큼.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그걸 우리는 신데의 디코이를 활용한다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>뭐 이건.. 크라운 있는 사람들은 다 알만한 내용이라 이쯤하고,&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그래서 크라운이 없는 우리에게 중요한건 뭐냐?</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><font color=\"#ff0000\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">\"핵심1 : 버스트 조절 타이밍이 모든것을 결정한다.\"</span></b></font></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b style=\"color:rgb(255,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">\"핵심2 : 신데의 디코이는 크없찐의 희망이다.\"</span></b><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><b><br></b></font></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b>(수정) 대충적을려고 했는데 그냥 장문으로 다 고쳐버리겠음.&nbsp;</b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b>제 디테일을 보시고 진정으로 이 글을 보고 도움 받기를 기원합니다.</b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>나또한 이 택택을 실행하면서 버스트 조절을 1초단위로 세세하게 조절했음.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>왜 그런지는 직접 해보면 안다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>택틱 설명 들어간다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>풀버를 신데와 헬름으로 돌아가며 쓰는데, 레후의 버스트를 신데에게 달자.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>돌덩이는 우선적으로 패줘야하는건 알지?&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>영상 내용에 맞게 설명하면, 일단 처음 나오는 따발총은 그냥 처맞아도 됨. 왜냐?&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>두번째 버스트 굴릴때 헬름 버스트로 피채우면 됨. 이거 또한 신데의 디코이를 활용하기 위해서임.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그리고 2페이즈 돌입 직후, 버스트를 바로 쓰면 안됨. 내가 짚어준 핵심을 잘 생각해야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>내가 아까 버스트or 풀버의 지속시간은 10초인걸 알려줬지?&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>2페이즈 들어가자마자 버스트를 쓰면 두번째 돌덩이가 나오고 따발총 패턴 들어올때&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>신데가 포커싱 되지 않고, 나같은 경우는 라피나 레후가 따발총을 맞아서, 엄폐물의 체력을&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>소모시키거나 체력소모를 해야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>근데 조금 뜸을 들이고, 베히가 첫 돌덩이를 던질타이밍때 풀버를 킨다? 그러면 풀버끝나는 타이밍에&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>맞게 신데에게 따발총이 들어갈거고, 그건 신데가 디코이로 상쇄 시켜 줄것이다. 물론 이 택틱은 신데가&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>잘 큰 상황이어야 가능한 말이지만, 앞서 말했듯이 준비물 자체가 잘키운 신데이기 때문에 그냥&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>내가 쓴 택택 그대로 설명하겠음.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이렇게 한차례 패턴이 끝났고, 돌덩이 패턴 2번을 넘기고 나면&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>나오는게 전격 저지 2개의 패턴임. <b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">이때가 진짜 졸라 중요함.</span></b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>버스트를 적절히 굴리고, 재빨리 레후로 톡톡이 치면서 1버의 라피 버스트를 켜줘야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>아까 말했듯이 우리는 크라운의 사기적인 상시공증이 없기때문에, 여기서 1버만큼은 켜줘야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>나같은 경우는 일반 신데로는 안되고, 라피 1버만을 킨 신데평타로 2개의 전격저지가 시간에 맞게</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>부셔질 정도로 키움. 이게 안되면 안된다고 봐야함.</p><a class