ank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그리고 또 따발총 날라오는데 나한텐 또 라피한테 따발총 날라오더라. 내가 택틱 실행하면서</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>캐릭 육성을 조금씩 더 하니까 이렇게 되더라. 여기서는 어쩔수 없다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이제는 진짜 조심해야함. 우리는 헬름의 버스트가 있기때문에 라피 잡고 안심하면서&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>처맞되, 죽기직전에 엄폐해서 엄폐물로 체력 유지하셈. 아니면 그냥 뒤져버린다 ㅋㅋ</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>원래 나도 신데가 쳐맞았는데 라피 장비 렙업 1.2 더해주니까 안되더라.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이타이밍에 신데가 따발총 맞으면 감사합니다 하면서 넘어가자.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>설명 졸라 어렵네... 해보면 뭔말인지 알거임.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그리고 두번째로 나오는 전격저지는 그냥 풀버켜도 된다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>계속 졸라 패주자.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그 이후 떼거리 저지는 풀버켜진 라피로 맘껏 부셔주면 된다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그리고 이건 육성마다 달라서 따로 설명 안했지만, 신데와 라피는 장탄관리를 적절히 해줘야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>안그러면 전격저지때 바보같은 신데렐라가 장전 쳐해서 그대로뒤진다 ㅋㅋ</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>또 하나는 후반부 돌격후에 떼로 나오는 저지 때 라피가 장전해서 또 귀찮아질수 있음.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>그 이후 또하나의 핵심 활용. 떼거리 저지 이후 베히가 그로기 걸리는데,&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>이때 쓸수있는 버스트는 헬름임. 바로 써버리면 베히모스 전기구이 패턴때</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>버스트 꺼져서 뒤져버리니까, 타이밍 맞게 좀 뜸들이면서 써야함.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>또 하나의 디테일은, 헬름은 가한 피해량 비례로 힐이기 때문에</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>ㄱㄴ 저지패턴때 시간이 좀 남는데 ㄱ과 ㄴ사이에 시간이 남는데 이때&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>성실하게 베히를 패줘야 라피가 그브가 안뒤짐.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>전기구이 패턴때 라피나 그브의 피가 많이 갈렸으면 좀 위험해짐.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>2번째 전기구이때 베히를 죽이거나 아니면 피 1로 살거나, 우리가 죽거나다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;</a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>여기까지 왔으면 축하합니다. 몇번 트라이 해보면 <b>\"깰 수도 있을겁니다.\"</b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><b><br></b></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b>나역시 364k면 그렇게 낮은 투력은 아닌거같다만 다뒤지고 방어형인 신데만&nbsp;</b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><b>살아서 버저비터 성공한거다.&nbsp;</b></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><b><br></b></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>내가 가지고 있던 디테일이 훨씬 더 많을텐데 기억이 안나네... 너무 뽕차서&nbsp;</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>뇌가 녹은듯...</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><b><br></b></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>물론 내가 되도 않는 억지택틱으로 깬 것일 수도 있겠지만, 화이팅하세요.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>2주년입문이지만 너무 힘들었습니다. 그러면 저는 이제 35지 밀러 가보겠습니다.</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p>화이팅</p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a></p><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a></div><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://youtu.be/G7ZZmkXDsVM?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\"></a>",
